History of clinically significant pulmonary toxicity or interstitial lung disease/pneumonitis;
Uncontrolled cardiovascular disease including congestive heart failure NYHA class III-IV;
Significant hepatic impairment (bilirubin > 1.5× ULN or AST/ALT > 2.5× ULN);
